videos.headline: Neal hopes team can help uplift Vegas
videos.description: Golden Knights forward James Neal says he had tickets for Sunday's concert in Las Vegas but didn't go because of an early skate and discusses the impact he hopes the new NHL team will have on the city.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Neal hopes team can help uplift Vegas) 2017/10/06
